whole_object: When the traffic light turned green, the trash bin was still pondering whether to stay or take out itself.
single_object:
- Bicycle: This bicycle decided to take a brake from pedaling around town.
- Trash can: Garbage day is the trash can's moment to lid up the street!
- Traffic light: Always up for a game of red light, green light – without moving an inch.
- Car: I would tell you a car joke, but I'm still working on the delivery.
- Building: The building felt stories high when it finally got over its fear of elevators.
- Tree: The tree never leaves a conversation without branching into new topics.
